# Room Template Generator

Skill for generating room code with common patterns, door connectivity, event triggers, and standard layout for SCPB.

## When to Use

Use this skill when:
- Creating a new room for the facility
- Adding room to map generation
- Setting up room events and triggers
- Defining door connections
- Creating special room types (SCP containment, offices, etc.)

## Generate Room Command

```blitzbasic
; Command format:
; GenerateRoom name$, zone$, [options]
;
; Examples:
; GenerateRoom "MyOffice" LCZ
; GenerateRoom "Containment_173" HCZ scp="173"
; GenerateRoom "ExitZone" EZ exit=True
```

## Room Template Structure

```blitzbasic
; Generated room template
; Run: GenerateRoom "Room_Name" ZONE [options]

; Room constants
Const ROOM_MY_ROOM% = 500  ; Next available ID

; Room data structure
Type RoomData
    Field ID%
    Field Name$
    Field Zone%
    Field DoorCount%
    Field DoorTargets[6]
    Field DoorTypes[6]
    Field EventCount%
    Field Events[10]
    Field Commonness%
    Field MinSize%
    Field MaxSize%
    Field Requires%
    Field Excludes%
End Type

; Room configuration
Global Room_MyRoom.RoomData
```

## Basic Room Template

```blitzbasic
Function GenerateRoom_MyRoom()
    ; Create room data
    Room_MyRoom.RoomData = New RoomData
    Room_MyRoom\ID = ROOM_MY_ROOM
    Room_MyRoom\Name$ = "My Room"
    Room_MyRoom\Zone% = ZONE_LCZ
    Room_MyRoom\DoorCount% = 4
    Room_MyRoom\Commonness% = 10
    Room_MyRoom\MinSize% = 2
    Room_MyRoom\MaxSize% = 4
    Room_MyRoom\Requires% = 0
    Room_MyRoom\Excludes% = 0

    ; Door connections (to be filled by MapSystem)
    For i = 0 To 5
        Room_MyRoom\DoorTargets[i] = -1
        Room_MyRoom\DoorTypes[i] = DOOR_STANDARD
    Next

    Return Handle(Room_MyRoom)
End Function

Function LoadRoom_MyRoom()
    ; Unload existing room
    UnloadCurrentRoom()

    ; Load room mesh
    roomMesh = LoadMesh("GFX/map/my_room.b3d")
    SetParent roomMesh, RoomRoot

    ; Load collision mesh
    roomCollider = LoadMesh("GFX/map/my_room_col.b3d")
    SetParent roomCollider, RoomRoot

    ; Set up doors
    SetupDoors(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Set up SCP (if any)
    SetupRoomSCP(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Set up items
    SetupRoomItems(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Set up events
    SetupRoomEvents(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Set up lights
    SetupRoomLights(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Set room fog
    SetRoomFog(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Play ambient sound
    PlayRoomAmbient(ROOM_MY_ROOM)
End Function

Function UnloadRoom_MyRoom()
    ; Clean up room resources
    If roomMesh <> 0 Then FreeEntity roomMesh
    If roomCollider <> 0 Then FreeEntity roomCollider

    ; Unload NPCs in room
    UnloadRoomNPCs(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Unload items in room
    UnloadRoomItems(ROOM_MY_ROOM)

    ; Stop ambient sound
    StopRoomAmbient(ROOM_MY_ROOM)
End Function
```

## Containment Room Template

```blitzbasic
; SCP Containment Cell
; Run: GenerateRoom "Containment_XXX" HCZ scp="XXX"

Function GenerateRoom_Containment()
    room.RoomData = New RoomData
    room\ID = ROOM_CONTAINMENT_XXX
    room\Name$ = "Containment Cell XXX"
    room\Zone% = ZONE_HCZ
    room\DoorCount% = 2
    room\Commonness% = 5  ; Rare
    room\MinSize% = 1
    room\MaxSize% = 1

    ; Heavy containment door
    room\DoorTypes[0] = DOOR_HEAVY
    room\DoorTypes[1] = DOOR_STANDARD

    ; SCP info
    room\SCP_ID% = NPC_SCP_XXX
    room\ContainmentActive% = True
    room\BreachChance% = 10

    Return Handle(room)
End Function

Function LoadRoom_Containment()
    ; Base room
    roomMesh = LoadMesh("GFX/map/containment_standard.b3d")

    ; Containment features
    LoadContainmentChamber()

    ; SCP mesh (if active)
    If RoomContainsSCP(ROOM_CURRENT)
        LoadSCPModel()
        PositionEntity scp\obj, 0, 0, 0
    End If

    ; Warning signs
    LoadWarningSigns()

    ; Intercom
    LoadIntercom()
End Function

Function SetupContainmentEvents()
    ; Breach event
    AddRoomEvent("SCP_BREACH", EVENT_SCP_BREACH, 0, 10)  ; 10% chance

    ; Containment failure
    AddRoomEvent("CONTAINMENT_FAIL", EVENT_CONTAINMENT_FAIL, 100, 0)

    ; SCP escape
    AddRoomEvent("SCP_ESCAPE", EVENT_SCP_ESCAPE, 0, 0)
End Function
```

## Office Room Template

```blitzbasic
; Standard office/workspace
; Run: GenerateRoom "Office_Standard" LCZ type="office"

Function GenerateRoom_Office()
    room.RoomData = New RoomData
    room\ID = ROOM_OFFICE_STANDARD
    room\Name$ = "Office"
    room\Zone% = ZONE_LCZ
    room\DoorCount% = 2
    room\Commonness% = 15
    room\MinSize% = 2
    room\MaxSize% = 3

    ; Furniture
    room\Furniture$ = "desk,chair,filing_cabinet,computer"
    room\KeycardLevel% = 0

    ; Items that can spawn
    room\PossibleItems$ = "keycard_red,medkit,flashlight,battery"

    ; Can contain dead scientist
    room\DeadBodyChance% = 30

    Return Handle(room)
End Function

Function LoadRoom_Office()
    ; Base office mesh
    roomMesh = LoadMesh("GFX/map/office_standard.b3d")

    ; Add furniture
    LoadFurniture("desk", 0, 0, -5)
    LoadFurniture("chair", 0, 0, -4)
    LoadFurniture("filing_cabinet", 5, 0, 0)
    LoadFurniture("computer", 0, 1, -5)

    ; Dead body (random chance)
    If Rand(1, 100) < GetRoomData("DeadBodyChance")
        SpawnDeadScientist()
    End If

    ; Items
    SpawnRoomItems()
End Function

Function SpawnRoomItems()
    items$ = GetRoomData("PossibleItems")
    count = Rand(1, 3)

    For i = 1 To count
        item$ = PickRandomItem(items$)
        If Not RoomHasItem(item$)
            SpawnItem(item$, RandomPositionInRoom())
        End If
    Next
End Function
```

## Corridor Room Template

```blitzbasic
; Standard corridor
; Run: GenerateRoom "Corridor_LCZ" LCZ type="corridor"

Const CORRIDOR_STRAIGHT% = 0
Const CORRIDOR_TURN% = 1
Const CORRIDOR_T_JUNCTION% = 2
Const CORRIDOR_CROSS% = 3

Function GenerateRoom_Corridor()
    room.RoomData = New RoomData
    room\ID = ROOM_CORRIDOR_STRAIGHT
    room\Name$ = "Corridor"
    room\Zone% = ZONE_LCZ
    room\DoorCount% = 4  ; Can connect to multiple
    room\Commonness% = 30  ; Very common
    room\MinSize% = 1
    room\MaxSize% = 1

    ; Corridor type
    room\CorridorType% = CORRIDOR_STRAIGHT

    ; Lighting
    room\LightLevel% = 80
    room\Flickering% = False

    ; Hazards
    room\HazardChance% = 5

    Return Handle(room)
End Function

Function LoadRoom_Corridor()
    ; Select mesh based on corridor type
    Select GetRoomData("CorridorType")
        Case CORRIDOR_STRAIGHT
            mesh$ = "corridor_straight"
        Case CORRIDOR_TURN
            mesh$ = "corridor_turn"
        Case CORRIDOR_T_JUNCTION
            mesh$ = "corridor_t"
        Case CORRIDOR_CROSS
            mesh$ = "corridor_cross"
    End Select

    roomMesh = LoadMesh("GFX/map/" + mesh$ + ".b3d")

    ; Lights along corridor
    SetupCorridorLights()

    ; Hazard (random)
    If Rand(1, 100) < GetRoomData("HazardChance")
        SpawnCorridorHazard()
    End If
End Function

Function SetupCorridorLights()
    ; Place lights every few units
    For i = 0 To 10
        x# = i * 5 - 25
        CreateLightPoint(x#, 2, 0)
    Next
End Function
```

## Exit/Entrance Room Template

```blitzbasic
; Room leading to surface or elevator
; Run: GenerateRoom "Elevator_LCZ" LCZ exit=True

Function GenerateRoom_Elevator()
    room.RoomData = New RoomData
    room\ID = ROOM_ELEVATOR_LCZ
    room\Name$ = "Elevator Shaft"
    room\Zone% = ZONE_LCZ
    room\DoorCount% = 2
    room\Commonness% = 5

    ; Elevator info
    room\IsElevator% = True
    room\ElevatorTarget% = ZONE_HCZ
    room\RequiresKeycard% = True
    room\KeycardLevel% = KEYCARD_RED

    Return Handle(room)
End Function

Function LoadRoom_Elevator()
    ; Elevator room mesh
    roomMesh = LoadMesh("GFX/map/elevator_room.b3d")

    ; Elevator doors
    elevatorDoors = LoadMesh("GFX/map/elevator_doors.b3d")

    ; Elevator panel
    LoadElevatorPanel()

    ; Keycard reader
    LoadKeycardReader(KEYCARD_RED)
End Function

Function UseElevator(targetFloor%)
    ; Check requirements
    If GetRoomData("RequiresKeycard")
        If Not PlayerHasKeycard(GetRoomData("KeycardLevel"))
            ShowMessage("Requires keycard level " + GetRoomData("KeycardLevel"))
            Return False
        End If
    End If

    ; Animation
    PlayAnimation("elevator_doors_open")
    Wait(60)
    PlayAnimation("elevator_travel")
    Wait(120)
    PlayAnimation("elevator_doors_open")

    ; Change room
    ChangeRoom(GetRoomData("ElevatorTarget"))

    Return True
End Function
```

## Complete Room Generator

```blitzbasic
; Main generator function
Function GenerateRoom%(name$, zone$, options$ = "")
    ; Parse options
    roomType$ = ParseOptionStr(options$, "type")
    scp$ = ParseOptionStr(options$, "scp")
    exit% = ParseOption(options$, "exit")
    danger% = ParseOption(options$, "danger")

    ; Generate file
    file$ = "Generated_Room_" + name$ + ".bb"
    file = WriteFile(file$)

    ; Write header
    WriteLine file, "; Generated Room: " + name$
    WriteLine file, "; Zone: " + zone$
    WriteLine file, "; Generated: " + Date()
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; Write constants
    WriteLine file, "; === CONSTANTS ==="
    WriteLine file, "Const ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + "% = " + GetNextRoomID()
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; Write type definition
    WriteLine file, "; === ROOM DATA ==="
    WriteLine file, "Type RoomData"
    WriteLine file, "    Field ID%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field Name$"
    WriteLine file, "    Field Zone%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field DoorCount%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field DoorTargets[6]"
    WriteLine file, "    Field DoorTypes[6]"
    WriteLine file, "    Field Commonness%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field MinSize%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field MaxSize%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field Requires%"
    WriteLine file, "    Field Excludes%"
    WriteLine file, "End Type"
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; Write Generate function
    WriteLine file, "; === GENERATION ==="
    WriteLine file, "Function GenerateRoom_" + name$ + "%()"
    WriteLine file, "    room.RoomData = New RoomData"
    WriteLine file, "    room\ID = ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ""
    WriteLine file, "    room\Name$ = """ + name$ + """"
    WriteLine file, "    room\Zone% = ZONE_" + Upper(zone$) + ""
    WriteLine file, "    room\DoorCount% = 4"
    WriteLine file, "    room\Commonness% = 10"
    WriteLine file, "    room\MinSize% = 2"
    WriteLine file, "    room\MaxSize% = 4"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Door connections"
    WriteLine file, "    For i = 0 To 5"
    WriteLine file, "        room\DoorTargets[i] = -1"
    WriteLine file, "        room\DoorTypes[i] = DOOR_STANDARD"
    WriteLine file, "    Next"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    Return Handle(room)"
    WriteLine file, "End Function"
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; Write Load function
    WriteLine file, "; === LOADING ==="
    WriteLine file, "Function LoadRoom_" + name$ + "%()"
    WriteLine file, "    UnloadCurrentRoom()"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Load room mesh"
    WriteLine file, "    roomMesh = LoadMesh(""GFX/map/" + Lower(name$) + ".b3d"")"
    WriteLine file, "    SetParent roomMesh, RoomRoot"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Load collision"
    WriteLine file, "    roomCollider = LoadMesh(""GFX/map/" + Lower(name$) + "_col.b3d"")"
    WriteLine file, "    SetParent roomCollider, RoomRoot"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Setup doors"
    WriteLine file, "    SetupDoors(ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ")"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Setup items"
    WriteLine file, "    SetupRoomItems(ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ")"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "    ; Setup events"
    WriteLine file, "    SetupRoomEvents(ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ")"
    WriteLine file, "End Function"
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; Write Unload function
    WriteLine file, "; === UNLOADING ==="
    WriteLine file, "Function UnloadRoom_" + name$ + "%()"
    WriteLine file, "    If roomMesh <> 0 Then FreeEntity roomMesh"
    WriteLine file, "    If roomCollider <> 0 Then FreeEntity roomCollider"
    WriteLine file, "    UnloadRoomNPCs(ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ")"
    WriteLine file, "    UnloadRoomItems(ROOM_" + Upper(name$) + ")"
    WriteLine file, "End Function"

    CloseFile(file)

    Print "Generated: " + file$
    Return True
End Function
```

## Usage Examples

```blitzbasic
; Basic room
GenerateRoom "Staff_Breakroom" LCZ

; SCP containment
GenerateRoom "Containment_173" HCZ scp="173"

; Exit room
GenerateRoom "Surface_Exit" EZ exit=True

; Corridor
GenerateRoom "Main_Corridor" LCZ type="corridor"

; Danger room
GenerateRoom "Armory" HCZ danger=True
```

## Room Configuration

```blitzbasic
; Room zones
Const ZONE_LCZ% = 0  ; Light Containment
Const ZONE_HCZ% = 1  ; Heavy Containment
Const ZONE_EZ% = 2   ; Entrance Zone
Const ZONE_SURFACE% = 3

; Door types
Const DOOR_STANDARD% = 0
Const DOOR_HEAVY% = 1
Const DOOR_CHECKPOINT% = 2
Const DOOR_ELEVATOR% = 3
Const DOOR_EXIT% = 4

; Keycard levels
Const KEYCARD_NONE% = 0
Const KEYCARD_RED% = 1
Const KEYCARD_BLUE% = 2
Const KEYCARD_GREEN% = 3
Const KEYCARD_OMEGA% = 4
```

## Quick Reference

| Option | Effect |
|--------|--------|
| `type=office` | Office with furniture |
| `type=corridor` | Corridor layout |
| `type=containment` | SCP containment cell |
| `scp="XXX"` | Contains SCP-XXX |
| `exit=True` | Is exit/elevator room |
| `danger=True` | High hazard chance |
| `zone=HCZ` | Set zone (LCZ/HCZ/EZ) |
